Name: Tetropunk
About the game: Do not miss the chance to play a bestseller among the classic games! Clear out the lines and stay calm while the passions in the game are heating up, because this addictive puzzle is not as simple as it might seem. Also, a pleasant soundtrack will not allow you to miss a second! A simple and exciting game for all ages. Features: 2 game modes, 10 difficulty levels, leaderboard.
